ஓர்சோறு. (c.) வடித்தபானையிலோரவிழுங்கிடையாது. a single grain of rice will not be found in a well cleaned vessel. கலவுமிதின்றாலோரவிழ்தட்டாதா? if you eat twelve marcals of husks  
will not one grain of rice touch (your teeth?) i. e. if you take much trouble  
will you not derive some benefit?  
