வி. a. to loosen  
slacken  
untie  
unpack  
unfasten  
unsew  
முடியவிழ்க்க  
2. to cause to open  
as the sun opens flowers. humming insects are also described by poets as opening the flowers. மலரச்செய்ய  
3. to solve an enigma  
unriddle  
explain a difficulty  
விடுகதைவிடுவிக்க. அவன்காலால்முடிந்ததைக் கையாலவிழ்க்கக்கூடாது. what he has bound with his foot  
none can unbind with their hands; i. e. he is a crafty man whose schemes no body  
though ever so skilful  
can defeat